<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>In Zend/Console/Getopt.php line 611 :</p>

<p>$lines[] = $linepart;</p>

<p>$lines has not been initialized as an empty array before the foreach loop.
So, if $this-&gt;_rules is empty, the foreach never loops, $lines remain undefined, and a warning is sent at line 613 :</p>

<p>foreach ($lines as $linepart) {</p>

<p>I guess a simple :</p>

<p>$lines = array();</p>

<p>at line 585 should resolve the issue.</p>

